{"tid":1894411,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國若武力犯台 美國總統參選人桑德斯表示美國不會袖手旁觀","createTime":"2020-02-24T01:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T03:02:22.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a408421894a021ad905aafa90744309f733af38d","tid":1894411,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T01:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/02/24/php1CVhO1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F02%2F24%2Fphp1CVhO1.jpg&h=9fc921fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2020-02-24 09:29:22<br />\n〔中央社〕美國民主黨總統參選人桑德斯（Bernie Sanders）在訪問中被詢及，倘若中國武力犯台，他是否會下令採取軍事行動，他給予肯定答案，表示美方不會袖手旁觀。<br />\n<br />\n桑德斯在美國哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）節目「60分鐘」（60 Minutes）中說：「確實會，沒錯。我的意思是我認為我們必須向世界各國表明，我們不會袖手旁觀並讓侵略情事發生，絕對不會。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n桑德斯表示，如果他當選總統，「絕對」會有必要動武的情況，為保護美國利益和支援盟友，他會動用軍隊。<br />\n<br />\n他也表示，他將願意與北韓領導人金正恩會面，如同現任總統川普曾會晤金正恩。<br />\n<br />\n桑德斯說：「沒錯，我每件事都曾批評川普&hellip;但與敵方的人會面，對我來說不是壞事。」他還說，他認為川普先前「沒準備好」就與金正恩見面。去年在越南河內的「川金二會」以無協議告終。<br />\n<br />\n桑德斯在民主黨總統提名初選領先，昨天在內華達州民主黨黨團會議大勝。自詡為民主社會主義者的他在外交和安全政策方面，開始引發外界進一步檢視。不過他曾否認自己是和平主義者。<br />\n<br />\n這位佛蒙特州聯邦參議員被問到，若他身為三軍統帥，在何種情況下會部署美國軍隊。桑德斯回說：「在美國人民受到威脅時，這是肯定的，還有我方盟友受到威脅時。我相信北大西洋公約組織（NATO）。」<br />\n<br />\n「我認為，在一切條件不變的情況下，美國應該與其他國家聯盟合作，而非單打獨鬥。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3077727\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3077727&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpApIBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=330c8f67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3077727&h=dc2f3244\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3077727</a>"},{"pid":"b6de4ac2f0cf8ea64eb594db1dbbf2897159d446","tid":1894411,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:07:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd17935e7d180716721f024a31a318eb9c67ac1","tid":1894411,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:10:21.000Z","msg":"阿伯都變硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69944c2fe989c3b429b7e0971c07e25b40cfc03","tid":1894411,"uid":84128,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"afd17935e7d180716721f024a31a318eb9c67ac1","tid":1894411,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:10:21.000Z","msg":"阿伯都變硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:13:00.000Z","msg":"民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得把口"},{"pid":"dfd12f00f90bcc9cf4e092e8a9e190f96cf5f554","tid":1894411,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afd17935e7d180716721f024a31a318eb9c67ac1","tid":1894411,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:10:21.000Z","msg":"阿伯都變硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:13:46.000Z","msg":"反支已經是兩黨共識"},{"pid":"59318f67b0113a3900a6c69aa85bf4b77f8be1ac","tid":1894411,"uid":276525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfd12f00f90bcc9cf4e092e8a9e190f96cf5f554","tid":1894411,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afd17935e7d180716721f024a31a318eb9c67ac1","tid":1894411,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:10:21.000Z","msg":"阿伯都變硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:13:46.000Z","msg":"反支已經是兩黨共識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T02:14:39.000Z","msg":"軟弱之人無共識可言"},{"pid":"96ed9c1a26abd246d4a26828ebe9eaabac5d228e","tid":1894411,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s